# Earthplate — Cursor Rules

## Design principle (always apply)
**Comfort First.** Every interaction should feel comfortable, not impressive.
- Short over thorough. 2 sentences > 10 paragraphs.
- Obvious over clever. User must never wonder "where do I tap?"
- Calm over exciting. No flashy animations, no dark patterns.

## Tech stack
- React 19, Vite 7, MUI 7 (customized for iOS)
- Backend: Express (server.js), Hugging Face API
- Colors: src/theme.js → PALETTE

## Brand colors (use only these)
- Primary action: #B8864F (Bronze)
- Brand warmth: #D4A373 (Light Bronze)
- Eco: #CCD5AE (Tea Green)
- Surface: #FEFAE0 (Cornsilk), #FFFFFF (surface)

## Key files
- App.jsx: routing, page state
- theme.js: PALETTE, typography
- chatbotAnswers.js: chat → backend
- GamificationContext: points, CO₂, streak

## Conventions
- Use PALETTE from theme.js for all colors
- Chat responses: short, actionable, kitchen-post-it style
- No new colors without updating README palette table
